name: El loco
description: Both the fall and the elevation are equally divine, they are part of a change in consciousness towards new enlightments, and the fool (Tarot) is the innocent force, the dynamic energy that permeates and plays with the whole magnitude of this being in transformation, its the opening of the punch changing chaotic risk, towards the drive and explosion of elevation. Analog inking and pointillism, with digital painting. 2299x1388px, 300dpi and 3.27mb.
